Review Text:
Had tried Paneer Butter Masala, Veg 65 and Chilly Paneer from this restaurant.
The above items were pretty average in taste. Paneer Butter Masala and Veg 65 were okay but the Chilly Paneer was below average. I was expecting a more of strong chilli flavor but it had very mild flavors and was a little tasteless.

I ordered 2 items kadhai paneer and paneer parantha. First of all i will talk about the paneer dish. It was a nice dish and gravy was well prepared so if u wish to eat paneer order this one for sure. Now i will talk about the parantha. It was like a plain parantha no stuffing it never looked or tasted like a paneer parantha so never order this ever from this place.

Really good on : Pricing - Quantity - Taste
I usually orders Paneer Biriyani which is great in taste and not spicy like others.¬†
Yesterday I ordered Paneer Biriyani and Mushroom 65. Mushroom 65 quantity is more than sufficient for 2 people and tasty too.¬†
Recommended for vegetarians.

A decent place to visit. This is especially for the vegetarians as it a pure veg restaurant. Decent ambience, nothing exemplary but with quick service and decent pricing, this is a place one can visit with friends and looking to just eat.
